                    React Building Styles with CSS Modules
                    Course Notes


                    Section 1 - Introduction
1 - Welcome
A quick welcome to the course and introduction to the instructor
There are a great many ways in which to use CSS with React
  - This course is intended to clarify the options
  - The syntax for CSS Modules with React will be tackled

2 - Course Prerequisites
There are some prerequisites to taking the course
  - Some React knowledge and experience is a must
  - Knowledge of components, state, props and structure is needed
  - Experience with JavaScript and ES6 syntax is needed
  - Being familiar with the command line and the npm package manager is recommended
  - The course is OS agnostic

3 - Using The Exercise Files
How to make use of the exercise files that are provided with the course



